with their families can opt for EB-5 Immigrant Investor Visa Program. The program was initiated in 1990 with the intention to bring global investors to USA to serve the economy and become a US Citizen. Applying for USA EB-5 Program, Individuals can relocate to USA with family on a permanent resident status leading to citizenship.\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-69e943f e-grid e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"69e943f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-585e2b3 ekit-equal-height-disable elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"585e2b3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/unemployment.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <div class=\"box-body\">\n                        \t\t  \t<p>A minimum investment of $ 800,000 in govt-approved commercial enterprises .<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n        <\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b8069c3 ekit-equal-height-disable elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"b8069c3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/job-offer.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <div class=\"box-body\">\n                        \t\t  \t<p>Compulsion to create minimum 10 permanent full-time jobs for qualified U.S. workers.<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n        <\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f7e9023 ekit-equal-height-disable elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"f7e9023\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elements